<br>
More than likely has not played much LDON and does not understand the point that Faulse was trying to make.<br>
<br>
In a DL group it's really easy to disband someone from your group and pick up someone else. There's always someone LFG there.<br>
<br>
In LDON you pick your group and once you start you're stuck with them. If someone disbands then you're a man short which can kill the possibility of reaching your goal. These dungeons are all about teamwork. So if you don't know who you're playing with it's a risk. Sometimes you develop friendships and sometimes you decide not to ever group with a particular person. It's a learning experience that can be fruitful or painful. That's how pickup groups go.<br>
<br>
So now somebody comes along and gives a heads up about some jerk that is not worth grouping with to help us all out, and the moron comes out to flame about what he should have done.<br>
Well if he knew ahead of time as we all now do, it is easy to click disband and get someone else BEFORE you get the adventure. After the adventure starts the choice gets tougher. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rpayne>rpayne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>New User</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(9/25/03 10:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2198.topic&index=38>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re:Evil Booblet</span><hr size=1> Dude, Vin!   Evilsoul Bloodspilla in the flesh here.  But Ive grown a bit from when I used to be in BoD and Black Reign.  Yeah its me, same owner. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rpayne>rpayne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>New User</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(9/25/03 10:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2198.topic&index=39>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re:Evil Booblet</span><hr size=1> By the way, rpayne and FaulseHope username is same guy.  Just this computer remembers me as rpayne and home computer remembers me as FaulseHope, just in case there was any confusion <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kenak>Kenak</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 41<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(9/25/03 11:06 am)</font><br>   <a 